idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu cakkhunā rūpaṃ disvā rajanīye rūpe na sārajjati, sakkoti cittaṃ samādahituṃ.
evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu khamo hoti rūpānaṃ. (1)
