evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu khamo hoti phoṭṭhabbānaṃ. (5)
imehi kho, bhikkhave, pañcahi dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu āhuneyyo hoti pāhuneyyo dakkhiṇeyyo añjalikaraṇīyo anuttaraṃ puññakkhettaṃ lokassā”ti.
navamaṃ.
